*《韩诗外传》(1952). Cambridge, Mass.: Harvard University Press.
*《陶潜诗选》 (1970). Oxford: Oxford University Press.
*与[[叶嘉莹|叶嘉莹]]共同翻译，《中国诗歌论集》 (1998). Cambridge, Mass.: Harvard University Asia Center.<ref>[http://news.nankai.edu.cn/xkhp/system/2013/10/23/000147974.shtml] {{Wayback|url=http://news.nankai.edu.cn/xkhp/system/2013/10/23/000147974.shtml |date=20170114060555 }}，序言。</ref>
